Author:
Vol / Page: 23
Edition:
Quote: THE INCONVENIENT `WINGY' [title] ... a lady sitting comfortably in a tram-car, saw a one-winged soldier hanging to a strap, and advised him thus : `You men should wait for a car that has seating accommodation.'
