Author: HILLIARD
Vol / Page: 123
Edition:
Quote: Dad cut his meat for him because his arm was in a sling ... Dad took him into the kitchen to meet ... the cook. `A wingie, I see,' Alf said. `Not that I know much about it - I was too old for the Boer War.'
